complete django auth system with user roles


incase of any dificulties installing contact me via https://nyagaka.com/blog/contact or 0745566505 or omundifelix30@gmail.com or contact@nyagaka.com



To run the project config your app by add environment variables

# SECRET_KEY=bbbnnnnnnfffgggrrr
# DEBUG=True
# EMAIL_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
# EMAIL_PORT=587
# EMAIL_USE_TLS=True
# EMAIL_HOST_USER=john.doe@gmail.com
# EMAIL_HOST_PASSWORD=mnfjytt56644888
# DEFAULT_FROM_EMAIL = john.doe@gmail.com

Go to your gmail and make app password replace
 EMAIL_HOST_USER with your email address
EMAIL_HOST_PASSWORD with your app password
DEFAULT_FROM_EMAIL with your email adddress

